description: API and app-local type hygiene
globs: apps/**/src/types/**/*,packages/app-core/**/*
alwaysApply: false
---

# Type placement

- `src/types/*` reflects **current** backend contract only — no speculative or legacy fields.
- Backend enum values must match exactly (no broad `string` unless API allows).
- Detail/list migrations: ID path params in routes/actions; name/search in query types only.
- Shared types → `packages/app-core` first; app-local only when role-specific.

Full guide: `docs/architecture/type-system.md` · ADR: `docs/decisions/adr-003-strict-type-placement.md`
